snippet.title: 🎾Tennis Tower🏰 - Full playthrough
snippet.description:
Play the game here: https://adriendittrick.itch.io/tennis-tower
Made with Edward Atkin: https://eatkin.itch.io/
No treasures mode: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MPq3Ey8FDCk

Tennis Tower is a game where you scale a 20-stories high tower. Each floor has an optional chest, which may help you complete further floors.

This game was made using the process of gamedev Tennis, where 2 devs throw a game at each other and add small things until a deadline is reached. If you're interested in trying gamedev tennis, consider joining this jam:
https://itch.io/jam/gamedev-tennis-game-jam
